               <p>HYMON LEVY. I am a <rs id="t18310217-237-viclabel1389" type="occupation">slop-seller</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-237-victim2202 t18310217-237-viclabel1389"></join>, in <placeName id="t18310217-237-crimeloc1390">Broad-street, Ratcliff</placeName>
