                     <interp inst="t18310217-237-person2204" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-constable. The prisoner is one of the sailors who was in a mob, in the highway - I took him at Ratcliff-cross, and found these trousers on him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. We went to go to the Admiralty - many of us were without clothes; I picked up the trousers in the crowd.</p>
